# =============================================================================
# school-ai-rag — TOP-LEVEL (direct) dependencies actually imported by the app.
#
# This replaces the previous 242-package UTF-16 `pip freeze` (which contained
# many unrelated developer-machine packages, e.g. google-genai, bcrypt,
# fonttools). Only packages the application source actually imports are kept.
#
# Pinned/locked output lives in requirements.txt.
# For the lightweight local boot (API + health, no heavy ML stack) use
# requirements-core.txt instead.
#
# Verified against imports in:
#   app/api.py, app/cli.py, app/llm/groq_client.py,
#   app/prediction/service.py, app/prediction/router.py,
#   app/rag/{loader,splitter,indexer,retriever}.py,
#   app/quiz/*, app/analyze/*
# =============================================================================

